# Marker file. Presence of this `.mvn` directory at the repo root makes
# Maven set `${maven.multiModuleProjectDirectory}` to the repo root for
# every invocation, regardless of which sub-aggregator is being built
# (integrations/jvm, integrations/jvm/eclipse, …). Submodule pom.xml
# files reference the root-level checkstyle.xml and eclipse-formatter.xml
# via that property.
